ssport_visa/出發前必睇-各國-護照有效期-例表/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gotrip.hk%2Ftravel_hacker%2Fpassport_visa%2F%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E5%89%8D%E5%BF%85%E7%9D%87-%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B-%E8%AD%B7%E7%85%A7%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E6%9C%9F-%E4%BE%8B%E8%A1%A8%2F&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=7bdcaf85\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gotrip.hk/travel_hacker/passport_visa/出發前必睇-各國-護照有效期-例表/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/DetailNews.php?id=ADsRYxEpA3QMLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2FDetailNews.php%3Fid%3DADsRYxEpA3QMLA&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=74557419\" target=\"_blank\">http://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/DetailNews.php?id=ADsRYxEpA3QMLA</a><br />\n<br />\n上面啲文話逗留期間有效就得<br />\n信唔信得過？</blockquote><br />\n入得<br />\n不過航空公司職員好大機會唔俾你 check-in<br />\n你要企硬話無問題<br />\n等佢哋放人<br />\n如果唔係連機都無得上"},{"pid":"f02eeb43685851284c9fd54632e34f71de292359","tid":55000,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1613b59decdf9112c4e6eb5e88a847d68c80588","tid":55000,"uid":16940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"留名等結果"},{"pid":"a725b73445a606ece3126191b38ba164cb337c7e","tid":55000,"uid":8461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.gotrip.hk/travel_hacker/passport_visa/出發前必睇-各國-護照有效期-例表/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gotrip.hk%2Ftravel_hacker%2Fpassport_visa%2F%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E5%89%8D%E5%BF%85%E7%9D%87-%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B-%E8%AD%B7%E7%85%A7%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E6%9C%9F-%E4%BE%8B%E8%A1%A8%2F&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=7bdcaf85\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gotrip.hk/travel_hacker/passport_visa/出發前必睇-各國-護照有效期-例表/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://tr