/>\n等佢哋放人<br />\n如果唔係連機都無得上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1268994dfc4d4642ef1011d22a51e441346e196","tid":55000,"uid":60205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"日本得 台灣就唔得 算你好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0cb950fa29574978981070186f6acf2c9289f97","tid":55000,"uid":19371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.gotrip.hk/travel_hacker/passport_visa/出發前必睇-各國-護照有效期-例表/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gotrip.hk%2Ftravel_hacker%2Fpassport_visa%2F%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E5%89%8D%E5%BF%85%E7%9D%87-%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B-%E8%AD%B7%E7%85%A7%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E6%9C%9F-%E4%BE%8B%E8%A1%A8%2F&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=7bdcaf85\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gotrip.hk/travel_hacker/passport_visa/出發前必睇-各國-護照有效期-例表/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/DetailNews.php?id=ADsRYxEpA3QMLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2FDetailNews.php%3Fid%3DADsRYxEpA3QMLA&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=74557419\" target=\"_blank\">http://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/DetailNews.php?id=ADsRYxEpA3QMLA</a><br />\n<br />\n上面啲文話逗留期間有效就得<br />\n信唔信得過？</blockquote><br />\n入得<br />\n不過航空公司職員好大機會唔俾你 check-in<br />\n你要企硬話無問題<br />\n等佢哋放人<br />\n如果唔係連機都無得上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢真係衝出黎柒，有次我去日本，去8日，本passport剩返11日期，個地勤照俾我check in，只不過提醒我就到期，記得回港後去拎過本新嘅<br />\n（事前打咗電話去日本領事館同cx問，話無問題）"}]}